text: Mitsutake Makita (born 1908, date of death unknown) was a Japanese ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Japanese male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Japan Category:Ski jumpers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sakhalin Oblast
